snippet.title: HeroWarz Official -  CBT Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Sign-Up Today: https://register.koggames.com/herowarz

Humanity's greatest strengths have been found in its darkest corners. Maya is trapped, and if she can't be found, all hope is lost.

The time has come for us to work together and defend our homelands from annihilation. The apocalypse is close, and if we don’t act now, then our world as we know it will be washed away...

HERO, we need YOU! Join today, and help fight to keep humanity alive!

CBT Begins May 18th, 2016!

___________________________

HeroWarz is the ultimate action RPG where you select and cultivate unique heroes to build your own personal assault force. Get ready for the most addicting, fast-paced, action-packed battles, and let this one-of-a-kind gaming experience breathe excitement back into into your 'virtual' reality.

Website - http://herowarz.net/
Facebook - https://facebook.com/HeroWarzGlobal/
Twitter - https://twitter.com/HeroWarzGlobal
Google+ - https://plus.google.com/u/0/b/1155247...

___________________________
